    "name": "史莱姆冒险战",
    "steam_appid": 2166820,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2166820/extras/92686298aca9624be671312adcb80637.avif?t=1739754998\" width=392 height=76 /></span><br><br><br><strong>【  QQ交流群：916334297  】</strong><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2166820/extras/92686298aca9624be671312adcb80637.avif?t=1739754998\" width=392 height=76 /></span><br><br><br>《史莱姆冒险战》是一款轻度rogue、策略、塔防游戏。可以自由建设道路和建设丰富的buff塔的特别塔防游戏。玩家扮演史莱姆女王对抗入侵的冒险者。<br>这是一款非传统的塔防游戏，你需要巧妙的布置敌人进攻的路径和塔的方位。buff塔形成的数值优势，这可以让你不借助外部强化也能赢得游戏胜利。<br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >史莱姆与冒险者</h2></strong><br><br>传说中史莱姆是很弱小的生物。这是一个史莱姆与冒险者的斗争，消灭入侵的冒险者保卫史莱姆！拯救史莱姆女王，解锁角色和立绘。每一个角色有不同的数值和机制。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2166820/extras/48b81e092eb051c479a30754f6d92dbe.avif?t=1739754998\" width=739 height=240 /></span><br><br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >核心选择</h2></strong><br>每一场战有？种核心选择。每一种核心会改变 你的这一局的游玩模式。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2166820/extras/8d38105c2a80e20fee69077619524c6e.avif?t=1739754998\" width=512 height=256 /></span><br><br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >BUFF塔</h2></strong><br>Buff塔是这个游戏的亮点。你可以通过BUFF塔加强你的女王或者攻击塔，达成的游戏通关。也可以不使用buff塔进行传统的塔防布置。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2166820/extras/5aae21009f1901a344e2e7dc62603046.poster.avif?t=1739754998\" width=800 height=492 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2166820/extras/5aae21009f1901a344e2e7dc62603046.webm?t=1739754998\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2166820/extras/5aae21009f1901a344e2e7dc62603046.mp4?t=1739754998\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >规划</h2></strong><br>和以往的塔防不同，这里的攻击塔拥有血量。所以规划布局进行防守。同一种塔，放置的位置不同甚至会决定你的成败。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2166820/extras/dfccde48773d5a3622c5d85207ef5239.poster.avif?t=1739754998\" width=658 height=466 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2166820/extras/dfccde48773d5a3622c5d85207ef5239.webm?t=1739754998\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2166820/extras/dfccde48773d5a3622c5d85207ef5239.mp4?t=1739754998\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >自由道路</h2></strong><br><br>在游戏中你可以铺设自己的道路。根据每局游戏时间的递进你可以获得你能铺设的道路格子数量。游戏过程中可以随意改变道路的布局以此来辅助你的策略。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2166820/extras/70356a2fdda5bf975499388d53d31043.poster.avif?t=1739754998\" width=800 height=690 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2166820/extras/70356a2fdda5bf975499388d53d31043.webm?t=1739754998\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2166820/extras/70356a2fdda5bf975499388d53d31043.mp4?t=1739754998\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >随机与决策</h2></strong><br><br>从随机抽取的塔中选择你需要的塔。你可以选择攻击型的塔增加攻击单位，也可以选择buff型的塔强化你的攻击单位。<br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >强化升级</h2></strong><br><br>如果你打不过，可以选择在主界面升级你的攻击塔和女王，守护住每一个地下城。<br>（如果你喜欢挑战，完全可以不场外升级通关。）",
